<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>John Doe - Mentor Profile</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2em;
        }

        .profile {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2em;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .profile img {
                width: 150px;
                height: 150px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 1em;
            }

            .profile h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
                color: #013f6b;
            }

            .profile p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 2em;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #013f6b;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="John Doe">
        <h1>John Doe</h1>
        <p>John is an expert in Web Development with 10+ years of experience in building dynamic, user-friendly websites. He specializes in JavaScript frameworks, backend services, and modern web technologies.</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Home")" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
